_json.gridTitle: 50 Stunning Breakfast Nook Ideas You Have to See
_json.description: If you thought you didn’t have space for a breakfast nook, think again. This picture shows that you could fit a small breakfast nook in just about any space. In many homes, an awkward space like this might go unused, but a custom-made table and chairs could fit well. This table attaches to the wall, so there’s only one actual leg supporting it, a big way to save on space while providing support.
